 * Macro name: Beshaba and Tymora's Fate 
 * Select the tokens you want to involve, run the macro, and the name + image of the randomly chosen token will appear. 
 * NPC names appear as "????" for players, while GMs always see full names.
 * One reveal part has a delay of 0.5 sec (500 msec) â€“ adjust if needed.
 */

// Array of funny descriptions
